node.title: Patrick De La Cerda murder: Inside the case
node.description: In 2018, the Deltona, Florida, man was newly engaged and planning for his wedding until he was tragically gunned down at his home.
node.content: ["In 2018, the Deltona, Florida, man was newly engaged and planning for his wedding until he was tragically gunned down at his home.", "Patrick De La Cerda and his fianc\u00e9e Jessica Devnani were looking forward to their future wedding. The couple met on a dating app called Plenty Fish in June 2017."]
